snippet.title: Oak Hill: New 2D INDIE GAME Trailer (English Version)
snippet.description:
In this new 2D adventure you play as Theo, a dog! After dying, you find yourself in Oak Hill, the dimension between life and death. You will have to face many challenges to reach your best friend Harriet to say goodbye and to move on.

Coming soon.

Trailer Music By: Scott Buckley, Soar. (www.scottbuckley.com.au) / Creative Commons CC BY 4.0
